// Polearms (MAG/RARE): hide all
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (bar OR vou OR scy OR pax OR hal OR wsc OR 9b7 OR 9vo OR 9s8 OR 9pa OR 9h9 OR 9wc OR 7o7 OR 7vo OR 7s8 OR 7pa OR 7h7 OR 7wc) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:

// Crossbows (MAG/RARE): show only (hxb OR 8hx OR 6hx), hide the rest
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (hxb OR 8hx OR 6hx) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]: %NAME%{%NAME%}%CONTINUE%
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (lxb OR mxb OR rxb OR 8lx OR 8mx OR 8rx OR 6lx OR 6mx OR 6rx) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:

// Wands (MAG/RARE): show all
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (wnd OR 9wn OR 7wn OR ywn OR 9yw OR 7yw OR bwn OR 9bw OR 7bw OR gwn OR 9gw OR 7gw) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]: %NAME%{%NAME%}%CONTINUE%

// Assassin Claws (MAG/RARE): show only (ktr OR 9ar OR 7ar OR axf OR 9xf OR 7xf OR skr OR 9qr OR 7qr), hide the rest
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (ktr OR 9ar OR 7ar OR axf OR 9xf OR 7xf OR skr OR 9qr OR 7qr) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]: %NAME%{%NAME%}%CONTINUE%
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (wrb OR ces OR clw OR btl OR 9wb OR 9cs OR 9lw OR 9tw OR 7wb OR 7cs OR 7lw OR 7tw) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:

// Sorc Orbs (MAG/RARE): show only (ob5 OR oba OR obf), hide the rest
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (ob5 OR oba OR obf) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]: %NAME%{%NAME%}%CONTINUE%
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (ob1 OR ob2 OR ob3 OR ob4 OR ob6 OR ob7 OR ob8 OR ob9 OR obb OR obc OR obd OR obe) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:

// Amazon Bows & Spears (MAG/RARE): show (am1 OR am2 OR am6 OR am7 OR amb OR amc) and hide the rest
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (am1 OR am2 OR am6 OR am7 OR amb OR amc) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]: %NAME%{%NAME%}%CONTINUE%
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (am3 OR am4 OR am5 OR am8 OR am9 OR ama OR amd OR ame OR amf) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:

// Arrow/Bolt Quivers (MAG/RARE): hide all
ItemDisplay[FL8_ACTIVE FL8_OUTSIDE FL8_UNID (cqv1 OR cqv2 OR cqv3 OR aqv1 OR aqv2 OR aqv3) (MAG OR RARE) !FL8_EXEMPT]:
// ===============================
// FL8 town/shop safety pass
// Strict hides apply outside town; town/shop keeps unid gear visible for checking.
// ===============================
ItemDisplay[(ARMOR OR WEAPON OR QUIVER) (TOWN OR SHOP) !ID !UNI !RW !SET FILTLVL>7]: %NAME%{%PURPLE%Decrease Your Filter Level in Settings to Display It All The Time%NL%%WHITE%Outside the Town/In the Fight Field it is Going to be %RED%HIDDEN%NL%WARNING%WHITE%: At Current Filter LVL this item is shown %RED%ONLY %WHITE%in Town%CL%%NAME%}%CONTINUE%

